    "date": "2019-10-28T14:36:30Z",
    "text": "End Double Taxation of Successful Civil Claims Act \n\nThis bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to expand the deduction from gross income (above-the-line deduction) for attorney fees and court costs to include such fees and costs paid in connection with any legal action involving a civil claim (currently, limited to actions involving unlawful discrimination, the False Claims Act, and Medicare payments)."
